    {
      "type": "text", "id": "legend_insight", "x": 1792, "y": 468, "width": 342, "height": 130,
      "text": "The code (step 7) travels through\nthe browser but is worthless alone.\nOnly the back-channel exchange\n(step 9) — where the client proves\nitself with its secret — yields the\naccess_token. Stealing the code\nalone is not enough.",
      "originalText": "The code (step 7) travels through\nthe browser but is worthless alone.\nOnly the back-channel exchange\n(step 9) — where the client proves\nitself with its secret — yields the\naccess_token. Stealing the code\nalone is not enough.",
      "fontSize": 13, "fontFamily": 3, "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#334155", "backgroundColor": "transparent", "fillStyle": "solid",
